trans-unit.source: Represents a declaration for an instance constructor of a type.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en deklarasjon for konstruktøren en forekomst av en type.

trans-unit.source: CodeConstructor can be used to represent a declaration of an instance constructor for a type.
trans-unit.target: CodeConstructor kan brukes til å representere en deklarasjon av en forekomstkonstruktør for en type.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeConstructor> to declare a static constructor for a type.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeConstructor>til deklarere en statisk konstruktør for en type.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeConstructor>

trans-unit.source: If the constructor calls a base class constructor, set the constructor arguments for the base class constructor in the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor.BaseConstructorArgs%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis konstruktøren kaller en basisklasse konstruktør, angir du konstruktørargumenter for basisklassen konstruktør i den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor.BaseConstructorArgs%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor.BaseConstructorArgs%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the constructor overloads another constuctor for the type, set the constructor arguments to pass to the overloaded type constructor in the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor.ChainedConstructorArgs%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis konstruktøren overlappinger en annen konstruktør for typen, angi konstruktørargumenter som sendes til overbelastet Typekonstruktøren i den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor.ChainedConstructorArgs%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor.ChainedConstructorArgs%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of base constructor arguments.
When the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor> overloads a base class constructor, this collection contains any arguments to pass to a base class constructor.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor>overlastingene basisklassen-konstruktøren denne samlingen inneholder noen argumenter som sendes til en basisklasse konstruktør.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor>

trans-unit.source: To call a base class constructor with no arguments, set a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression> containing an empty string ("") to this collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil kalle en basisklasse konstruktør uten argumenter, kan du angi en <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression>som inneholder en tom streng ("") i denne samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpressionCollection"></xref> that contains the base constructor arguments.
Gets the collection of chained constructor arguments.
When the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor> overloads another constructor of the same type, this collection contains any arguments to pass to the overloaded type constructor.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor>overlastingene en annen konstruktør av samme type, denne samlingen inneholder noen argumenter som sendes til overbelastet Typekonstruktøren.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeConstructor>

trans-unit.source: To call a constructor for the current type with no arguments, set a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression> containing an empty string ("") to this collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil kalle en konstruktør for gjeldende uten noen argumenter, kan du angi en <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression>som inneholder en tom streng ("") i denne samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpressionCollection"></xref> that contains the chained constructor arguments.
